9-06-11T17:10:05.000Z","msg":"講得好<br />\n<br />\n黑警重裝，如箭在弦，精祌由高度戒備，必不能久<br />\n我哋人多玩法多，時攻時守，佯守實攻，四方八面<br />\n和理非又扮勇武，勇武又唱下金天鵝唱下聖詩，草木皆兵也！"},{"pid":"4b92a2e45d177b504479d0d4eddf1d151bcd141e","tid":1204524,"uid":93479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T17:12:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfe19d07bcf1ce54e3b02b1412212df3ec24f21a","tid":1204524,"uid":167648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T18:37:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9543294e107fe54d458f6664b087c73c1155ebb1","tid":1204524,"uid":50835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T18:38:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yUeQsAU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyUeQsAU.jpg&h=c5b2b13e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f3462dbb16c8959c30cbddcb12661af8eda2e620","tid":1204524,"uid":16796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T18:43:51.000Z","msg":"最重要唔好戀戰"},{"pid":"a47c8094357a84443ac943ebf75b2b13236b0333","tid":1204524,"uid":85980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T18:47:05.000Z","msg":"Be Water!!!!!!!<br />\n<br />\n唔好意思借借位!<br />\n宗教理念未必一致, 但目標係一樣!!! <br />\n上街，卻似無法撼動政府的立場，我們還能作甚麼呢？在這個漸趨黑暗的日子，求你賜你的子民勇氣、信心及忍耐，堅守拒絕謊言、與受壓逼者同行、在絕望中活出美善以照亮別人的底線。<br />\n<br />\n願弟兄姊妹不分你我一同禱告，願上主憐憫。<br />\n<br />\n香港基督教教牧聯署籌委會 <br />\n早禱會<br />\n<br />\n日期: 2019.6.12<br />\n時間: 7:30-8:30<br />\n地點: 政府總部外<br />\n講員: 邢福增院長 <br />\n<br />\n <img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://scontent.fbne3-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/62512634_2342108942501590_5474578908500197376_n.jpg?_nc_cat=103&amp;_nc_eui2=AeEEa8YKWC2Gbx6sFNSWJsGbZqiS8-kUk1bxTcvnK_UysHrZhr-x4fU8Ij_0QaaJBLCdYfLUYM_w3BjyUukX-Qfi5L_voDS80mhrazWKb5MGFA&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fbne3-1.fna&amp;oh=2c2cb76e2ffcaadf2b7d8c45d9337214&amp;oe=5D8A46F8\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fbne3-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F62512634_2342108942501590_5474578908500197376_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D103%26_nc_eui2%3DAeEEa8YKWC2Gbx6sFNSWJsGbZqiS8-kUk1bxTcvnK_UysHrZhr-x4fU8Ij_0QaaJBLCdYfLUYM_w3BjyUukX-Qfi5L_voDS80mhrazWKb5MGFA%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fbne3-1.fna%26oh%3D2c2cb76e2ffcaadf2b7d8c45d9337214%26oe%3D5D8A46F8&h=db7c7c69&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E5%9F%BA%E7%9D%A3%E6%95%99%E6%95%99%E7%89%A7%E8%81%AF%E7%BD%B2%E7%B1%8C%E5%A7%94%E6%9C%83-2323884767657341/?tn-str=k*F\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%259F%25BA%25E7%259D%25A3%25E6%2595%2599%25E6%2595%2599%25E7%2589%25A7%25E8%2581%25AF%25E7%25BD%25B2%25E7%25B1%258C%25E5%25A7%2594%25E6%259C%2583-2323884767657341%2F%3Ftn-str%3Dk%2AF&d=TV1mljVccv2Dt1EdWC3TiQsTF5hDypdTwPi8eTnvKzQ%3D&h=2f79e57b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E5%9F%BA%E7%9D%A3%E6%95%99%E6%95%99%E7%89%A7%E8%81%AF%E7%BD%B2%E7%B1%8C%E5%A7%94%E6%9C%83-2323884767657341/?tn-str=k*F</a>"},{"pid":"827b7fafc80ac2f77d02b6745a6160d659a43a47","tid":1204524,"uid":36088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T18:52:02.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"557361e1433990236e976e9c2b06d665deba273b","tid":1204524,"uid":63017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T18:56:02.000Z","msg":"<span st